pull_request.title: nginx update
pull_request.body:
- Update nginx code version
- Switch nginx to use OpenSSL3 & oqsprovider
- Update OpenVPN following upstream integration of https://github.com/OpenVPN/openvpn/pull/278
- Align use of DEFAULT_GROUP config variable in subprojects
- Trigger re-build of ossl3 demo (oqsprovider) for IETF Hackathon taking in https://github.com/openssl/openssl/pull/20486 and https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/oqs-provider/pull/123 (moving this PR from draft ideally only after closing https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/oqs-provider/issues/126)
- Disable haproxy (see https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/oqs-demos/issues/182#issuecomment-1479029246)
